VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-81cb-a863-fd2f70e82904', 'Brat skewers', 'üå≠', NULL, 'Dinner', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cdldw1rgplj/?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["1 onion","1 green bell pepper","Salt","Pepper","Garlic","6 oz beer","Brats","Provolone cheese"]', 'Slice onion and green bell pepper and cook them up in a hot skillet. Season with salt, pepper, and garlic, and add in beer to help caramelize. Put brats on a skewer and grill over direct heat. Once brats are almost done cooking, top with provolone cheese and cook until melted. Top brats with peppers and onions and enjoy.', 1760731829780, 1760731829780, 0);
