VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-8176-8b5f-e74f19bc3c6b', 'Ground beef uglies', 'üêÆ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.bigoven.com/recipe/uglies/2579333', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["1 pound ground beef, venison, or elk","1/2 cup yellow onion, finely diced","1/2 cup green or red pepper, finely diced","1/2 cup favorite BBQ sauce, finely chopped","1 cup shredded cheese of choice","1 package crescent roll dough","Salt and pepper to taste"]', '1. Preheat oven to 375¬∞F (190¬∞C).
