VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-815a-a00c-fabf86960bae', 'Sloppy Joes ', 'üçî', NULL, 'Dinner', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/CgHtGaJgjqt/?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["2 lbs ground beef","Beef rub (seasoning to taste)","1 onion, finely diced","3 cloves garlic","4 tbsp tomato paste","2 tbsp apple cider vinegar","2 tbsp Worcestershire sauce","2 tbsp mustard","1 cup beef broth","Cheese","Burger buns"]', 'Season 2 lbs of ground beef with your favorite beef rub and form 2-3 large burgers. Smoke them for about 15 mins over indirect heat, then sear them off over direct heat to form a nice crust. Remove burgers and put them in a skillet and break them up. Cook for about 4-5 mins then remove. Saut√© 1 finely diced onion and 3 cloves of garlic for about 4 mins. Add in 4 tbsp tomato paste, 2 tbsp apple cider vinegar, 2 tbsp Worcestershire, 2 tbsp mustard and 1 cup of beef broth. Add the beef back in and mix thoroughly. Top with cheese and a bun and enjoy. These are quick easy meals and are even better the next day!', 1760731829780, 1760731829780, 0);
