VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-8182-b809-e1ba140d5056', 'Paxton PP Meal Ground Beef', 'üêÑ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["1 onion, chopped","fresh minced garlic to taste (3-6 cloves)","1 1/4 cups chopped carrots (pretty small)","1 1/4 cups chopped celery (pretty small)","2 lbs ground beef","2 cups jasmine rice","4 cups beef or chicken stock","1 tablespoon salt","2 teaspoons garlic powder","1.5 teaspoons dried basil","1.5 teaspoons dried parsley","1/2 teaspoon pepper","3 bay leaves","1 bunch cilantro"]', 'Brown ground beef then add onions and garlic and cook until onions are soft. Add carrots and celery, and cook down with a splash of stock, check on and stir every ~5 mins. Cover while the veggies soften and add a splash of broth when needed. After veggies soften, add the rice, stock, and season as needed. Then add the bay leaves and bring to a boil. Once boiling lower to a simmer and cook covered for 15 minutes or until all liquid is absorbed. Add chopped cilantro.', 1760731829780, 1760731829780, 0);
