VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-8137-ac68-e9949688f7f8', 'Sourdough Christmas Star', '‚≠ê', NULL, 'Snack', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cki_CqgJU63/?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["2 1/4 cups kamut flour or 2 1/2 cups all-purpose flour","2 tbsp sugar","1 tsp baking powder","1/2 tsp baking soda","1 tsp salt","1/2 cup butter","1 cup milk","1/2 cup sourdough discard","1/2 cup butter (for filling)","1/2 cup sugar (for filling)","1/2 cup brown sugar","2 tsp cinnamon","1 egg","Coarse sugar for topping"]', 'Stir together flour, sugar, baking powder, baking soda and salt. Grate butter on top and mix together to form a crumbly mix. Add milk and discard, mix to form a cohesive dough. Knead for a few minutes until soft. Place in bowl and let rise for around 4 hours on the counter and then an additional overnight ferment in the fridge (optional). Melt filling ingredients together in a pot. Cut dough into four sections. Roll out each section, adding filling to the first three layers. Place the final layer on top. Cut into 16 sections as seen in video. Twist away from one another to form the star limbs. Beat an egg and brush on top. Sprinkle with coarse sugar.', 1760731829781, 1760731829781, 0);
