VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-8195-bdfe-f41801ab363a', 'Chimichurri Wings ', 'üêî', NULL, 'Dinner', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cg4kadwg3_f/?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["Wings","Salt","Pepper","Garlic","1 tbsp corn starch","Cherry wood","1/4 cup parsley","1/4 cup cilantro","3 cloves garlic, minced","1/2 lemon, juiced","1 tbsp red wine vinegar","1/4 cup olive oil","1 tsp salt","1 tsp pepper","1 tsp crushed red pepper"]', 'Season wings with salt, pepper, garlic and add in 1 tbsp of corn starch to help crisp up the skin. Smoke wings for 30 mins using cherry wood. Make fresh chimichurri: combine parsley, cilantro, minced garlic, lemon juice, red wine vinegar, and olive oil with salt, pepper, and crushed red pepper. Move wings over direct heat flipping every couple of mins until they hit an internal temp of 190F. Toss the wings in the chimichurri and enjoy!', 1760731829781, 1760731829781, 0);
