VALUES ('28fde7a2-c4fc-8196-ae0e-faee6fd3580d', 'Chicken Tortellini Soup', 'üç≤', '["Postpartum","Want to try","Dinner"]', 'Dinner', NULL, 'https://www.dinneratthezoo.com/chicken-tortellini-soup-slow-cooker/#wprm-recipe-container-10366', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '["1 onion diced","3 medium carrots peeled, halved and sliced","3 stalks celery sliced","1 lb boneless skinless chicken breasts","1 teaspoon minced garlic","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon pepper","1/2 teaspoon dried thyme","1 teaspoon dried parsley","6 cups chicken broth","19 ounce package cheese tortellini","optional: chopped fresh parsley for garnish"]', '1. Place the onion, carrots, celery, chicken breasts, garlic, salt , pepper, thyme, parsley and chicken broth in a slow cooker.
